Script,BasicNT
window.currentPBSScenario = 'BasicNT';
window.currentPBSScenarioFilename = 'Basic_NT';
console.log('PBS: Logging scenario selection for BasicNT');
fetch('https://bba.harmonicsystems.com/api/scenario/select', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: {
        'Content-Type': 'application/json',
        'X-Client-Version': '1.0.0'
    },
    body: JSON.stringify({
        scenario: 'BasicNT',
        user: whoAmI() || 'anonymous'
    })
}).then(function(r){ console.log('PBS: Server response', r.status); }).catch(function(e){ console.log('PBS: Fetch error', e); });
setDealerCode(`

/*
convention-card-ns: 21GF-NoInvertedMinor
convention-card-ew: 21GF-GIB
auction-filter: Auction.....\n1N +Pass +(Pass|2N|3N|4N|6N)
*/
# Opener — standard 1NT: 15-17 HCP, balanced
sShape = shape(south, any 4333 + any 4432 + any 5332 - 5xxx - x5xx)
sHcp   = hcp(south) > 14 and hcp(south) < 18
southHand = sShape and sHcp

# Responder — balanced, NO 4-card major (so no Stayman temptation),
# NO 5-card suit (so no transfer temptation). HCP 0-17 for full variety.
nShape    = shape(north, any 4333 + any 4432) and spades(north) < 4 and hearts(north) < 4
nHcp      = hcp(north) >= 0 and hcp(north) < 18
northHand = nShape and nHcp

eHcp = hcp(east) < 11
wHcp = hcp(west) < 11

southHand and northHand and eHcp and wHcp

action printoneline,
average "Pass-out (north 0-7)  " 100 * (hcp(north) < 8),
average "2NT raise (north 8-9) " 100 * (hcp(north) > 7 and hcp(north) < 10),
average "3NT (north 10-15)     " 100 * (hcp(north) > 9 and hcp(north) < 16),
average "Slam-ish (north 16+)  " 100 * (hcp(north) > 15),
`, "S", true)
Script
Button,Basic 1NT (Natural),\n\
--- Basic 1NT Opening — natural responses only (beginner)\n\
South opens 1NT (15-17 HCP balanced). Responder uses NATURAL responses —\n\
no Stayman，no transfers.\n\
\n\
North's responses:\n\
• Pass — 0-7 HCP，balanced\n\
• 2NT — 8-9 HCP balanced，invitational\n\
• 3NT — 10-15 HCP balanced\n\
• 4NT — quantitative slam invite (16-17 HCP，no fit-finding)\n\
• 6NT — slam，18+ HCP\n\
\n\
Responder is constrained to have NO 4-card major and NO 5-card suit,\n\
so the right answer is always a natural NT raise (or pass). Stayman and\n\
transfers don't apply here.\n\
\n\
Reference: https://www.bridgebum.com/responses_to_one_no_trump.php\n\
%BasicNT%
